972
00:39:27,790 --> 00:39:29,830
Beraninya kamu mempermainkanku, beli atau tidak?

973
00:39:29,830 --> 00:39:31,670
Ya, ya, ya. Aku membelinya.

974
00:39:31,570 --> 00:39:34,410
[Kedai Teh Marga Feng]

975
00:39:31,790 --> 00:39:33,390
Hanya saja uang perakku

976
00:39:33,710 --> 00:39:35,630
disimpan di rumah istriku.

977
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:37,350
Aku sekarang tak punya banyak perak.

978
00:39:37,540 --> 00:39:38,270
Begini saja,

979
00:39:38,390 --> 00:39:40,510
